ently plays for [[Galatasaray]] and also played for [[Be\u015fikta\u015f Cola Turka]].\n\n==Stanford  statistics==\n{{NBA player statistics legend}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://web1.ncaa.org/stats/StatsSrv/careersearch|title=NCAA\u00ae Career Statistics|website=web1.ncaa.org|access-date=2016-05-21}}</ref>\n!Team\n!GP\n!Points\n!FG%\n!3P%\n!FT%\n!RPG\n!APG\n!SPG\n!BPG\n!PPG\n|-\n|2001-02\n|Stanford\n|35\n|208\n|43.4\n|42.4\n|77.3\n|2.0\n|2.2\n|0.7\n|0.4\n|5.9\n|-\n|2002-03\n|Stanford\n|32\n|270\n|38.9\n|39.5\n|78.3\n|1.5\n|2.2\n|0.6\n|0.2\n|8.4\n|-\n|2003-04\n|Stanford\n|34\n|229\n|31.6\n|33.5\n|74.3\n|3.0\n|1.9\n|0.9\n|0.3\n|6.7\n|-\n|2004-05\n|Stanford\n|35\n|184\n|38.1\n|35.0\n|78.8\n|2.9\n|1.9\n|1.0\n|0.1\n|5.3\n|-\n|Career\n|Stanford\n|136\n|891\n|37.5\n|37.3\n|77.0\n|2.4\n|2.0\n|0.8\n|0.3\n|6.6\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[Turkish women in sports]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.eurobasketwomen2005.com/en/default.asp?cid=%7B0AAC56F0-CCEF-488C-8BF7-BB5FDB0F7AF2%7D&pageID=&compID=%7BCF1BFB60-1462-4EB7-ABFD-6769D7079803%7D&roundID=3221&teamID=376&playerID=41399&season=2005&team2ID=376&player2ID \u015eebnem's Statistics]\n\n{{Galatasaray Women's Basketball Team current roster}}\n{{Galatasaray 2013\u201314 Euroleague Women champions}}\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kimyacioglu, Sebnem}}\n[[Category:1983 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American women's basketball players]]\n[[Category:Basketball players from California]]\n[[Category:American people of Turkish descent]]\n[[Category:Be\u015fikta\u015f women's basketball players]]\n[[Category:Galatasaray S.K. (women's basketball) players]]\n[[Category:People from Santa Clara, California]]\n[[Category:Power forwards (basketball)]]\n[[Category:Stanford Cardinal women's basketball players]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 2016 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Olympic basketball players of Turkey]]\n", "name_user": "Needemm", "label":